OL,5, A former Commonwealth youth gold       
OL,6, medallist tipped for world success says
OL,7, she suffered with bulimia for years as 
OL,8, a result of extreme criticism and      
OL,9, humiliating weigh-ins by her swimming  
OL,10, coaches.                               
OL,12,FPhoebe Lenderyou said she was just one 
OL,13,Fof many swimmers who would regularly   
OL,14,Fstarve themselves before being weighed 
OL,15,Fand that coaches would often blame poor
OL,16,Fperformance in the pool on weight gain.
OL,18,FOn one occasion, she said a group of   
OL,19,Fathletes were "tested" by coaches who  
OL,20,Fgave them chocolate cake and told them 
OL,21,Fthey had "failed" when they ate it.    
